CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 17 reads: "Two Beauties - Mrs. Robert L. Vann, Courier publisher and president, stands above the beautiful birthday cake presented to her by Miss Martha Tyson. The presentation was made at the party given for Mrs. Vann by more than six hundred friends in ballroom of the Sheraton Hotel, Monday night.  Tuesday, the cake was cut into more than two hundred pieces and shared by Mrs. Vann with her friends. - (Sockwell Photo)"
TitMainTitle: Jessie Vann standing behind table with three tiered birthday cake, in Penn Sheraton hotel
